sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Model / Application
    participant OnlineSvc as feast-online Service<br/>80/443 TCP
    participant FeatureServer as Feature Server Pod<br/>(FastAPI/Gunicorn)
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store<br/>(Redis/PostgreSQL)
    participant OfflineStore as Offline Store<br/>(DuckDB/PostgreSQL/Snowflake)
    participant Operator as Feast Operator<br/>(Go controller-runtime)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as Registry REST API<br/>6572/6573 TCP
    participant CronJob as CronJob Pod<br/>(ose-cli)
    participant Notebook as Kubeflow Notebook

    Note over Client,OnlineStore: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval
    Client->>OnlineSvc: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (80/443)<br/>Auth: OIDC Bearer or K8s SA token
    OnlineSvc->>FeatureServer: Forward to 6566/6567 TCP
    FeatureServer->>FeatureServer: Validate auth<br/>(SubjectAccessReview or OIDC JWT)
    FeatureServer->>OnlineStore: Query features<br/>Backend-specific protocol<br/>Auth: Credentials from Secret
    OnlineStore-->>FeatureServer: Feature values
    FeatureServer-->>OnlineSvc: JSON response
    OnlineSvc-->>Client: Feature vector response

    Note over CronJob,OfflineStore: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (CronJob)
    CronJob->>K8sAPI: kubectl exec into Feast pod<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>FeatureServer: Exec: feast materialize
    FeatureServer->>OfflineStore: Read historical features<br/>Backend-specific protocol<br/>Auth: Credentials from Secret
    OfflineStore-->>FeatureServer: Historical feature data
    FeatureServer->>OnlineStore: Write to online store<br/>Backend-specific protocol<br/>Auth: Credentials from Secret
    OnlineStore-->>FeatureServer: Write confirmation

    Note over Operator,Registry: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch FeatureStore CRs<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: FeatureStore CR event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployments,<br/>Services, ConfigMaps, RBAC<br/>HTTPS/443
    Operator->>Registry: GET /api/v1/permissions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (6572/6573)<br/>Auth: Intra-comm JWT (HS256)
    Registry-->>Operator: Permission definitions
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Reconcile ClusterRoleBindings<br/>from Feast permissions

    Note over Notebook,FeatureServer: Flow 4: Notebook Integration
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CRs<br/>(kubeflow.org/notebooks)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Notebook with feast-integration label
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read FeatureStore client ConfigMap
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Notebook ConfigMap<br/>with Feast client config
    Notebook->>OnlineSvc: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (80/443)<br/>Auth: User OIDC/K8s token
    OnlineSvc->>FeatureServer: Forward request
    FeatureServer-->>Notebook: Feature response
